sa pamilyang Chen!

552
00:25:01,730 --> 00:25:03,550
Ilang taon ka na bang gumagawa ng tinta?

553
00:25:03,550 --> 00:25:05,510
Gusto mo akong hamunin?

554
00:25:05,720 --> 00:25:07,920
Hindi mo ba alam ang lugar mo?

555
00:25:08,310 --> 00:25:09,200
Tama?

556
00:25:09,310 --> 00:25:10,720
-Tama!
-Oo nga!

557
00:25:11,110 --> 00:25:12,000
Tian Benchang!

558
00:25:12,640 --> 00:25:14,240
Dalhin mo ang iyong walang utang na loob na ama

559
00:25:14,240 --> 00:25:16,110
