naghahanap-kitang basura!

563
00:25:23,750 --> 00:25:24,720
-Oo!
-Tama!

564
00:25:24,720 --> 00:25:25,960
-Lumabas ka rito!
-Lumabas ka!

565
00:25:25,960 --> 00:25:27,160
Pasensya na, pasensya na.

566
00:25:27,350 --> 00:25:28,350
Padaanin mo ako. Ama!

567
00:25:28,350 --> 00:25:28,830
Ama.

568
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:29,720
Ama, Ama.

569
00:25:29,720 --> 00:25:30,520
Tumigil ka na sa pagmumura.

570
00:25:30,640 --> 00:25:32,750
Tigilan mo na ang pagmumura.
Kahit gaano mo pa sila ka-walang humpay na pagmumura,

571
00:25:32,750 --> 00:25:34,030
