572
00:25:34,030 --> 00:25:36,480
Hindi nila babaguhin ang kanilang mga gawi, Ama!

573
00:25:37,160 --> 00:25:38,200
Kalimutan mo na.

574
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:40,270
Hindi pwede! Hindi ko pwedeng hayaan na lang na matapos 'to.

575
00:25:44,070 --> 00:25:46,480
-Magaling!
-Magaling!

576
00:25:46,480 --> 00:25:47,480
Kayong mga Tian,

577
00:25:48,160 --> 00:25:48,960
