615
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:45,510
Oo, ayusin ang mga iskor.

616
00:26:45,510 --> 00:26:47,170
Tian Huai'an, Tian Benchang!

617
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:49,550
Ikaw na basura ng industriya ng tinta ng Huizhou!

618
00:26:49,550 --> 00:26:50,720
Lumabas ka rito!

619
00:26:50,750 --> 00:26:51,750
-Lumabas ka!
-Lumabas ka rito!

620
00:26:51,750 --> 00:26:53,080
Hindi ka lalabas, ha?

621
00:26:53,170 --> 00:26:54,440
Maaari kang patuloy na magtago,

622
00:26:54,510 --> 00:26:56,310
at patuloy kitang susumpain dito!

623
00:26:56,350 --> 00:26:58,030
Hangga't ako, ang Ikatlong Master Chen, ay narito,

624
00:26:58,030 --> 00:27:00,350
Wala kang magiging mapayapang araw!

625
00:27:00,480 --> 00:27:01,720
-Lumabas ka!
-Lumabas ka rito!

626
00:27:01,720 --> 00:27:02,510
Pangatlong Guro!

627
00:27:02,510 --> 00:27:03,070
Lumabas ka rito!

628
00:27:03,070 --> 00:27:04,000
Pangatlong Guro!

629
00:27:04,590 --> 00:27:05,390
Pangatlong Guro!

630
00:27:05,480 --> 00:27:06,310
Pangatlong Guro!

631
00:27:06,590 --> 00:27:08,070
Ikatlong Guro, Ikatlong Guro.

632
00:27:08,070 --> 00:27:08,880
Tagapamahala Zhen.

633
00:27:09,070 --> 00:27:10,510
Masamang balita! May nangyaring masama!

634
